data.title: Nina - Cavapoo Puppy for Sale in Louisville, OH
data.meta_description: Meet Nina! She is a Cavapoo that's just 10 weeks 2 days old old and looking for a wonderful family, like yours!
data.text:
Eric is a very handsome cavapoo, reddish wavy coat, mix with some Snow White pattern on his chest, head, tail and paws. He has great body posture, strong, straight and flexible.

Eric is gentle and sweet. He was taken by a young family for short time and was brought back to us, because the family had a big cat, the cat was aggressive to Eric…

We become more cautious afterwords. We are looking for a very nice and warm family for Eric. We wish our puppies can stay in a stable environment.

Eric has got 2 exams, he received his UTD vaccines and dewormed. We offer 60 days full refund warranty.

Ken is very tiny, weights only 3.8 lb now. His personality is easy, engaged and happy. I believe these are the best social skills. Ken can get the most care and love with his sweetness.

Ken is the second dog who falls in sleep while I am grooming him ( the first one is his dad).

Ken can become a perfect companion for a lovely family!

Ken has received 2 vet exams and dewormed. We offer his health certificate and 60 days full refund warranty.

Martin is a simple happy puppy, his tail can’t stop wagging when he sees us. He is gentle and sweet, loves people and the other dogs, he can make friends easily!

Martin is strong and energetic, he has got 2 vet exams, received utd vaccines and dewormed. We are looking for a warm friendly family for him. We offer 60 days full refund warranty.

Thank you!

Well, it was not so easy for me to take these picture for Mary! She was trying to stand or lay down closely to me, I only could catch some pics from her back.

Mary is a smart puppy, she is calm and observes well around. She understands people pretty well. I walk her in our small park without leash because she follows me nicely, doesn’t cause any problems.

Mary has a very thick brown coat. She may reach 10-12 lb.

Mary has got 2 vet exams and dewormed. We wish she can join a warm family. 60 days full refund warranty will be offered.

Thank you!

Apple is an extremely sweet companion! She follows me everywhere, never gets angry or upsetting.

Apple is always the first puppy running to me when I come home.

There are many dogs in our neighbourhood. Apple never barks ti any of them. She is calm, peaceful and confident.

Apple has a very beautiful wavy silky coat. She may reach to 10-12 lb.

We are looking for a friendly family for Apple.

Apple has received all 3 vet exams, additional dewormed, ear cleaning. We offer 60 days full refund warranty.

Rudy is a very sweet little guy. Enjoys his share of hugs and snuggles. Rudy will also be happy just sitting with you. Rudy is currently 4lbs and will be approximately 12lbs fully grown.

All my puppies are raised in my home right by my side. Family, friends and neighbors visit often to play. Paper and outdoor training is in progress.

Your baby will go home:

Current vaccination / dewormed Microchipped

30 days free pet insurance

Vet check/ certified

Go home goodie bag

ICA Registration form

additional pics and video upon request
